<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_182_r1l16"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> henn als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt wıe ewch geſagt ſey daʒ Jr vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_182_r1l17">dıe <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> / <expan>vnſıch<ex>er</ex></expan> vor vns ſein etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Nu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_182_r1l18"><expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> wır ʒu dıſen <expan>ʒeıt<ex>en</ex></expan> in ſunderheıt mıt eẅch <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> niht <expan>ʒuſchıke<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_182_r1l19"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> denn guts / <expan>Deſgleıche<ex>n</ex></expan> wır vns ʒu eẅch auch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſehen</expan> / VVeſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_182_r1l20"><expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> Jr <expan>kein<ex>en</ex></expan> der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> der eẅch in <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dechtnuſſ</expan> hett / VVenn vns dıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_182_r1l21">benennet <expan>wurde<ex>n</ex></expan> ſo <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> wır Jr red <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan> vnd eẅch denn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_182_r1l22"><expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> auch ein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> tun ob das an vns <expan>erford<ex>er</ex>t</expan> wurde / auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_182_r1l23"><expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> wır nıht wer dıe <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> ſınd / daʒ wır darcʒu nıht geant = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_182_r1l24"><expan>wurte<ex>n</ex></expan> können / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_182" id="90r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
